{"tid":1955325,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人投資 102 - 很技術分析的基本分析","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T01:11:08.000Z","uid":125976,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1b5b7f62221ca30e298f88df76b2568a9b9c6f","tid":1955325,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"冇錯，𠵱個 post 已經唔係 101，係 102，即係會難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人唔用基本分析，因為覺得佢好難量化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲分析員將佢複雜化咗，又話要考慮護城河、市盈率、ROE、公司文化 etc.<br />\n<br />\n成件事就好似啲傳統師父論八字咁，冇一啲統一啲嘅準則，各有各見解，好似乜都任你噏咁<br />\n<br />\n但其實基本分析嚟講，可以適當地將啲財務比率量化統計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n𠵱度我唔會教晒你每隻股點計，但可以舉隻股皇（700）做例子，𠵱隻好明顯係主要睇 P/E 啦：<br />\n<br />\n1. 喺 Yahoo Finance / 自己搵佢 5 - 10 年每日嘅股價<br />\n<br />\n2. 去 Aastocks / Etnet 搵佢 5 - 10 年每年嘅全年報表之中嘅每股盈利（請先化作港元）<br />\n<br />\n3. 將你所得幾年嘅每股盈利化作每日嘅每股盈利（interplote the data）<br />\n<br />\n6. 用股皇每日嘅股價除以  interplote 咗嘅每日每股盈利，去計出每日嘅 P/E<br />\n<br />\n7. 搵出𠵱幾年 P/E 嘅 min, mean, max, standard deviation<br />\n<br />\n8. 你知點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶嘅，上 殘.ga / 用支那牛牛，幫你計埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7rRm8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7rRm8J.jpg&h=178cba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mw6aCHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmw6aCHF.jpg&h=3c653dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁咪有圖睇啦，你鐘意喺幅屄圖上面畫線又好，整 regression channel 又好，加 BB, MACD, RSI, Ichimoku 又好，任你玩，夠 technical 未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2719c64966a3126d9dafa504bae11ecb2314f32e","tid":1955325,"uid":17330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"Hi bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 